content: Is there "GO Vote" graphics available to post on my family & friends FaceBook channels?

Hi <@1281266549226864807> after you download the Reach app, you will tap on Library, and then put "go vote" in the search box. you will see a screen like the picture I put here. If you put "vote" in the search box there will be more choices.
